<p>I work down the way from your office at UCSF in Mission Bay. I was suffering from similar problems and ended up petitioning to occupy some empty space we have. After some special meetings my request was approved and I now find myself in a large empty space with only a few other people about 20 meters away. In other words, peace, quiet, and a great view of the bay. Which equals me getting lots of work done and not wanting to even leave to go home.</p>

<p>Corporate thinking is backwards. Make your employees happy. Give them a space to think and don&#8217;t limit anything they can do.</p>

